WEBVTT

01:49.240 --> 01:52.039
What are the chances of my grandmother surviving?

01:53.160 --> 01:56.360
Right now, it looks like it's about 10%.

02:05.320 --> 02:06.120
Doctor,

02:07.160 --> 02:08.240
I beg you.

02:08.520 --> 02:09.400
Don't do this. Get up.

02:09.400 --> 02:10.720
Please save my grandmother.

02:10.720 --> 02:11.240
Yuanbao,

02:11.240 --> 02:12.240
get up first.

02:12.280 --> 02:15.480
I beg you to save my grandmother, doctor.

02:15.840 --> 02:17.320
Doctor, please.

02:17.520 --> 02:18.360
Whatever it takes,

02:18.360 --> 02:19.520
you must save her.

02:19.880 --> 02:21.079
Get up first.

02:21.920 --> 02:22.560
Get up.

02:23.320 --> 02:24.480
Rest assured,

02:24.640 --> 02:26.680
we will do our best.

02:27.040 --> 02:28.840
Even if there's only a 1% chance,

02:28.880 --> 02:30.440
we won't give up.

02:31.320 --> 02:32.079
But

02:32.480 --> 02:34.840
this surgery is quite difficult,

02:35.320 --> 02:37.320
and the treatment costs are not low.

02:37.440 --> 02:39.200
You must be mentally prepared.

02:46.880 --> 02:48.880
My family needs money urgently.

02:49.320 --> 02:50.520
Can you lend me some?

02:54.600 --> 02:55.640
Okay. It's fine.

02:56.040 --> 02:56.920
Thank you.

03:01.680 --> 03:02.360
Dandan,

03:02.640 --> 03:04.400
Are you well off right now?

03:04.440 --> 03:05.900
Can you lend me some money?

03:06.520 --> 03:07.840
Any amount is fine.

03:24.480 --> 03:27.280
Are you in pain, Grandma?

03:28.400 --> 03:30.930
The doctor said this disease is very painful.

03:31.840 --> 03:34.200
I wish I could bear the pain for you.

03:35.440 --> 03:37.079
You have to get better.

03:37.440 --> 03:39.570
We're all waiting for you to come home.

03:54.920 --> 03:59.079
Time to get up, sleepyhead.

04:05.680 --> 04:06.640
Grandma.

04:10.400 --> 04:11.320
Grandma.

04:14.720 --> 04:15.640
Grandma.

04:18.279 --> 04:19.560
Weren't you...

04:25.000 --> 04:25.720
Grandma.

04:27.080 --> 04:27.840
Grandma.

04:55.120 --> 04:55.880
Jingu.

04:57.040 --> 04:57.720
Yuanbao.

04:58.040 --> 05:00.100
My uncle is a cardiovascular doctor.

05:00.240 --> 05:01.680
He's very famous in Beijing.

05:01.680 --> 05:02.920
I've already told him.

05:02.920 --> 05:04.160
Maybe he can help.

05:05.560 --> 05:06.360
Really?

05:06.840 --> 05:07.640
That's great.

05:08.560 --> 05:09.680
Thank you, deskmate.

05:09.680 --> 05:12.040
What should I do now?

05:12.520 --> 05:13.520
You're welcome.

05:13.760 --> 05:15.690
But my uncle is usually quite busy.

05:15.960 --> 05:17.090
What we discussed is

05:17.320 --> 05:19.520
you first make a copy of Grandma's medical report

05:19.520 --> 05:21.320
and mail it directly to my uncle.

05:21.360 --> 05:22.680
Let him take a look first

05:22.680 --> 05:24.640
to see if there's a better treatment plan.

05:24.640 --> 05:26.280
If she can be transferred to Beijing,

05:26.280 --> 05:28.480
there might be a greater hope for a cure.

05:28.560 --> 05:29.160
Okay.

05:29.520 --> 05:30.320
Thank you.

05:30.480 --> 05:33.080
I'll go make a copy of the report right now.

05:33.240 --> 05:34.240
To make it faster,

05:34.640 --> 05:36.560
I'll send you the mailing address in a bit.

05:36.560 --> 05:37.800
Use expedited shipping.

05:37.800 --> 05:39.400
He should receive it the day after tomorrow.

05:39.400 --> 05:39.880
Okay.

05:39.960 --> 05:40.800
Okay. Thank you.

05:40.800 --> 05:42.400
Thank you. Thank you so much.

05:49.200 --> 05:51.159
You asked Mu Qingyun to enter the competition,

05:51.159 --> 05:52.420
but he flatly refused.

05:53.120 --> 05:55.280
Now Yuanbao's family is in trouble again.

05:55.280 --> 05:56.080
Meng Jingu,

05:56.520 --> 05:57.320
you should go.

05:57.520 --> 05:59.450
You'll do fine in the competition.

05:59.480 --> 06:01.940
And you even have a chance to win first place.

06:04.160 --> 06:04.890
May I come in?

06:05.160 --> 06:06.840
Mu Qingyun, why are you here?

06:09.480 --> 06:10.160
Mr. Tian,

06:11.040 --> 06:14.840
I have decided to participate in the National Physics Competition.

06:18.040 --> 06:19.960
Are you willing to admit it?

06:22.640 --> 06:23.770
I've made up my mind.

06:24.320 --> 06:25.440
But we just...

06:26.440 --> 06:27.970
convinced Meng Jingu to go.

06:28.640 --> 06:29.400
Meng Jingu,

06:29.880 --> 06:31.160
you decide.

06:34.720 --> 06:36.320
Have you thought it through?

06:36.400 --> 06:37.360
Yuanbao...

06:37.960 --> 06:39.090
I've made up my mind.

06:39.440 --> 06:40.720
As long as it can save Grandma,

06:40.720 --> 06:41.920
I'll do anything.

06:42.680 --> 06:43.880
It's been hard on you.

06:44.000 --> 06:44.930
As for the money,

06:45.520 --> 06:47.650
we'll figure something out together.

07:09.120 --> 07:10.920
Qingyun, I'm here in the UK,

07:11.040 --> 07:12.720
and I've visited many hospitals.

07:12.720 --> 07:13.920
The conclusion so far

07:13.960 --> 07:15.680
is that they don't recommend transferring Grandma.

07:15.680 --> 07:17.600
Don't worry, I'll keep looking.

07:17.960 --> 07:19.560
If I can't find a doctor in the UK,

07:19.560 --> 07:21.160
I'll look in other countries.

07:21.160 --> 07:23.080
Someone must be able to cure Grandma.

07:23.080 --> 07:23.880
Yes.

07:24.040 --> 07:26.000
Someone will be able to cure Grandma.

07:26.000 --> 07:27.120
I can't give up,

07:27.280 --> 07:28.540
and I can't break down.

07:28.760 --> 07:30.160
Yuanbao needs me right now.

07:30.160 --> 07:31.600
I have to be strong

07:31.800 --> 07:33.600
and take care of her for Grandma.

07:45.720 --> 07:46.640
You're back.

07:48.680 --> 07:49.240
Um...

07:50.280 --> 07:51.680
Well, I made some dishes.

07:51.720 --> 07:52.780
Go wash your hands.

07:55.200 --> 07:56.800
Where are my mom and grandpa?

07:57.280 --> 07:59.760
They need to stay at the hospital a bit longer.

07:59.760 --> 08:01.020
They'll be back later.

08:01.040 --> 08:02.840
What made you want to cook today?

08:05.280 --> 08:06.400
I was just thinking,

08:06.400 --> 08:08.880
since you guys are going to the hospital all day

08:08.880 --> 08:10.760
and I can't really help with anything,

08:10.760 --> 08:13.280
I'd cook some dishes for you.

08:14.680 --> 08:17.480
Don't just stand there. Go wash your hands and eat.

08:17.560 --> 08:19.600
We can take some to my mom later.

08:20.440 --> 08:22.000
I also want to see Grandma.

08:24.880 --> 08:26.080
You burned yourself.

08:29.200 --> 08:32.000
It's my first time cooking. Everyone gets burned,

08:32.000 --> 08:32.720
right?

08:43.760 --> 08:44.440
Yuanbao.

08:46.840 --> 08:47.680
I'm sorry.

08:50.880 --> 08:51.720
Yuanbao.

08:52.480 --> 08:53.560
I really didn't mean it.

08:53.560 --> 08:54.620
No need to explain.

08:55.680 --> 08:56.610
It's in the past.

09:02.520 --> 09:04.600
All right. Keep it dry tonight,

09:05.160 --> 09:07.620
and apply some ointment yourself tomorrow.

09:11.640 --> 09:12.560
Yuanbao.

09:13.600 --> 09:14.400
What's wrong?

09:14.600 --> 09:16.400
Ever since Grandma was hospitalized,

09:16.400 --> 09:18.460
have you not had a good night's sleep?

09:33.160 --> 09:34.000
Yuanbao,

09:34.200 --> 09:35.530
why are you so stubborn?

09:36.040 --> 09:38.080
Just let me go to the hospital with you.

09:38.080 --> 09:39.740
I haven't seen Grandma today.

09:39.840 --> 09:40.400
No need.

09:40.600 --> 09:42.520
Your hand is injured, and it's raining outside.

09:42.520 --> 09:43.960
I can go by myself.

09:44.240 --> 09:45.280
With such heavy rain outside,

09:45.280 --> 09:47.000
I definitely can't let you go alone, Yuanbao.

09:47.000 --> 09:48.260
Just let me go with you.

09:52.720 --> 09:53.720
Right now,

09:56.600 --> 09:58.260
you feel like a stranger to me.

10:01.560 --> 10:02.840
I want to go by myself.

10:07.880 --> 10:08.560
Yuanbao.

10:09.240 --> 10:11.080
Don't forget to tell Grandma

10:11.560 --> 10:13.560
that I'll be waiting for her at home.

10:14.720 --> 10:15.880
Okay, I got it.

10:16.640 --> 10:18.320
Be safe on your way, Yuanbao.

10:29.760 --> 10:31.560
You want me to sell the house now?

10:31.960 --> 10:33.360
Are you crazy?

10:34.040 --> 10:35.170
If we sell the house,

10:35.200 --> 10:36.840
where will Qingyun and I live?

10:36.840 --> 10:38.970
Do you expect us to live under a bridge?

10:39.280 --> 10:40.800
I never said I wouldn't care.

10:40.800 --> 10:43.080
And I never said we shouldn't get treatment.

10:43.080 --> 10:45.240
But do you know what the doctor said?

10:45.520 --> 10:47.000
The chance of Grandma surviving now

10:47.000 --> 10:48.240
is only ten percent.

10:48.640 --> 10:50.600
Do you know what that means?

10:51.080 --> 10:53.040
It means it's highly likely that in the end,

10:53.040 --> 10:54.880
we will lose both her and our money.

10:54.880 --> 10:56.610
I have no conscience? Mu Dabai,

10:56.720 --> 10:58.440
has your conscience been eaten by dogs?

10:58.440 --> 11:00.100
How could you say such a thing?

11:00.120 --> 11:00.840
Fine.

11:00.960 --> 11:03.320
Since you insist on bringing up the past today,

11:03.320 --> 11:05.160
I'll spell it out for you.

11:06.520 --> 11:09.360
We were supposed to be on duty the day of the incident.

11:09.360 --> 11:10.800
But Qingyun suddenly got

11:10.880 --> 11:12.960
acute pneumonia and had to be hospitalized.

11:12.960 --> 11:15.760
That's why we swapped shifts with the couple.

11:16.160 --> 11:17.600
We didn't do it on purpose.

11:17.600 --> 11:19.360
We didn't know an accident would happen that day,

11:19.360 --> 11:20.280
right?

11:20.480 --> 11:21.560
Besides,

11:22.080 --> 11:24.320
many things are just fate.

11:25.080 --> 11:26.000
It's been so many years,

11:26.000 --> 11:27.880
and we've done all we should do.

11:28.200 --> 11:29.880
What else do you want from me?

11:30.040 --> 11:32.480
Do we really have to pay with our lives

11:32.520 --> 11:33.760
to make it right?

11:47.000 --> 11:48.000
Yuanbao.

11:49.560 --> 11:50.840
Is it true?

11:51.400 --> 11:52.000
I...

11:52.920 --> 11:53.520
I...

11:54.000 --> 11:54.760
I...

11:55.640 --> 11:56.320
That day,

11:58.160 --> 11:59.620
they shouldn't have died.

12:00.680 --> 12:01.360
Right?

12:02.320 --> 12:02.960
I...

12:04.400 --> 12:05.080
Yuanbao,

12:08.360 --> 12:09.840
let me explain.

12:09.880 --> 12:10.480
We...

12:10.560 --> 12:12.920
we didn't mean to hide it from you.

12:15.560 --> 12:17.120
No.

12:19.640 --> 12:20.640
How could this happen?

12:20.640 --> 12:22.280
Why did this happen?

12:27.840 --> 12:28.840
Yuanbao.

13:08.320 --> 13:09.980
I'll leave the factory to you.

13:11.560 --> 13:12.560
How is it?

13:13.160 --> 13:14.560
I need to go to the factory.

13:14.560 --> 13:16.080
It's so late. I'll go with you.

13:16.080 --> 13:16.840
Let's go.

14:27.240 --> 14:28.080
You're back.

14:28.640 --> 14:30.080
Why didn't you answer the phone?

14:30.080 --> 14:31.040
I was so worried.

14:33.120 --> 14:34.480
You brought an umbrella.

14:34.480 --> 14:36.010
How did you still get so wet?

14:36.560 --> 14:37.400
I'm fine.

14:38.240 --> 14:39.200
How are you fine?

14:39.200 --> 14:40.160
You are completely soaked.

14:40.160 --> 14:41.200
Come on, let me help you change your clothes.

14:41.200 --> 14:42.240
Leave me alone.

14:46.560 --> 14:47.240
Yuanbao.

14:48.720 --> 14:49.760
What's wrong?

14:50.840 --> 14:52.040
I said I'm fine.

14:52.520 --> 14:54.250
Go back and get some rest early.

15:04.000 --> 15:04.760
Yuanbao.

15:04.920 --> 15:06.580
Then remember to dry your hair

15:06.600 --> 15:08.200
and take some cold medicine.

16:20.240 --> 16:21.370
You're still awake.

16:21.560 --> 16:24.600
Mom, why are you back so late?

16:26.960 --> 16:28.890
I stayed with Grandma a bit longer.

16:34.680 --> 16:36.120
Is Yuanbao back?

16:45.040 --> 16:46.080
Go to bed early.

16:54.200 --> 16:56.960
Did you get enough money

16:58.920 --> 17:00.560
for Grandma's medical bills?

17:00.560 --> 17:02.090
It's none of your business.

17:04.160 --> 17:05.760
Just focus on your studies.

17:07.000 --> 17:07.720
Mom,

17:08.720 --> 17:09.800
I mean,

17:09.960 --> 17:11.690
I still have some pocket money.

17:20.000 --> 17:20.930
What do you mean?

17:22.640 --> 17:24.400
You're just like your father.

17:24.880 --> 17:26.119
Besides pressuring me,

17:26.119 --> 17:27.640
what else can you two do?

17:28.319 --> 17:29.760
Mom, I mean...

17:29.760 --> 17:31.920
Mu Qingjun, look at yourself!

17:32.520 --> 17:34.160
You're not making progress in your studies,

17:34.160 --> 17:36.120
and you can't take care of yourself.

17:36.120 --> 17:37.650
You're almost 20 years old.

17:38.040 --> 17:39.080
For this family,

17:39.520 --> 17:40.640
I cook for you,

17:40.920 --> 17:41.960
I go to work,

17:42.080 --> 17:44.200
and I have to take care of everyone.

17:44.680 --> 17:47.480
We've been carrying a blood debt for you for over a decade.

17:47.480 --> 17:50.680
Even selling our house and land isn't enough to pay it off.

17:51.200 --> 17:53.080
What more do you want from us?

18:00.200 --> 18:02.720
Mom, what does this mean?

18:08.280 --> 18:09.920
You... you just said,

18:10.760 --> 18:11.960
for me?

18:12.200 --> 18:12.960
No.

18:13.320 --> 18:14.880
Did I hear that right, Mom?

18:15.040 --> 18:15.700
It's not...

18:15.800 --> 18:16.320
It's not...

18:16.320 --> 18:17.650
It's not like that, son.

18:20.200 --> 18:21.080
I just...

18:24.480 --> 18:25.960
It's not about Yuanbao

18:26.560 --> 18:28.240
and Grandma, is it?

18:28.240 --> 18:29.640
No, no, no.

18:29.920 --> 18:31.440
I'm sorry, son. No.

18:31.480 --> 18:32.960
Mom was too harsh.

18:33.000 --> 18:34.160
I didn't mean that.

18:34.240 --> 18:35.080
I mean...

18:35.360 --> 18:36.360
No, I...

18:36.600 --> 18:38.360
No, I'm just under too much pressure.

18:38.360 --> 18:40.160
I... I don't know...

18:40.720 --> 18:42.600
No. I'm sorry, son.

18:42.640 --> 18:43.640
Don't...

18:43.720 --> 18:45.920
Is it about Uncle Xiong and the others?

18:49.520 --> 18:51.040
No.

18:52.240 --> 18:54.080
No, it's not.

18:58.200 --> 18:59.240
So,

19:00.800 --> 19:03.330
the death of Uncle Xiong and Auntie back then,

19:06.480 --> 19:08.040
did it have to do with you

19:09.360 --> 19:11.640
and Dad, right?

19:13.440 --> 19:15.960
We didn't mean to do it.

19:17.200 --> 19:20.120
We really didn't mean to.

19:20.240 --> 19:22.520
Not on purpose.

19:23.680 --> 19:25.320
We didn't mean it.

19:25.360 --> 19:27.040
We didn't mean it.

19:28.960 --> 19:30.760
We didn't mean it.

19:30.800 --> 19:33.160
We didn't mean it.

19:38.160 --> 19:40.280
We didn't mean it.

19:41.200 --> 19:43.680
We didn't mean it.

19:49.960 --> 19:51.160
Actually, that day,

19:51.960 --> 19:54.420
your father and I were supposed to be on duty.

19:55.000 --> 19:57.880
But because you suddenly got acute pneumonia,

19:58.000 --> 20:00.000
we had to take you to the hospital.

20:00.640 --> 20:03.480
So we swapped shifts with Yuanbao's parents.

20:03.880 --> 20:05.760
But we never expected

20:06.360 --> 20:08.560
that an accident would happen that day.

21:30.080 --> 21:31.080
Yuanbao.

21:59.000 --> 21:59.800
Yuanbao.

22:01.040 --> 22:02.300
Auntie, yesterday...

22:04.400 --> 22:04.920
I...

22:05.000 --> 22:05.760
Auntie,

22:07.040 --> 22:08.000
I figured it out.

22:10.920 --> 22:12.080
I don't blame you.

22:14.080 --> 22:15.410
And I don't blame Mutou.

22:19.800 --> 22:20.600
Really?

22:23.120 --> 22:24.720
It was an accident after all.

22:25.760 --> 22:27.290
You didn't do it on purpose.

22:28.040 --> 22:29.520
And Mutou is innocent too.

22:29.720 --> 22:31.250
If there's anyone to blame,

22:32.800 --> 22:35.160
it's my parents' bad luck.

22:36.360 --> 22:37.000
No.

22:39.040 --> 22:40.000
It's us.

22:43.000 --> 22:44.440
It's our bad luck.

22:44.640 --> 22:45.960
Don't say that.

22:46.400 --> 22:47.640
What bad luck?

22:48.200 --> 22:50.200
I won't allow you to think like that.

22:51.200 --> 22:51.960
Auntie,

22:53.800 --> 22:56.760
thank you and Uncle for

22:57.200 --> 22:59.860
taking care of me and my grandma all these years.

23:00.760 --> 23:02.120
Without you,

23:04.320 --> 23:07.240
we wouldn't have had such a stable life for so long.

23:08.120 --> 23:09.160
But now,

23:11.200 --> 23:13.460
I don't want to be a burden to you anymore.

23:17.200 --> 23:18.760
You're still blaming us,

23:19.720 --> 23:20.720
and hating us,

23:21.960 --> 23:23.080
aren't you?

23:25.320 --> 23:26.160
Auntie,

23:27.400 --> 23:28.330
all these years,

23:29.560 --> 23:32.090
even though I've always called you Aunt Ning,

23:32.400 --> 23:33.880
in my heart,

23:34.840 --> 23:36.080
I've already treated you

23:36.080 --> 23:37.680
just like my own mother.

23:41.480 --> 23:42.840
I just said,

23:43.600 --> 23:44.720
I don't blame you.

23:45.560 --> 23:47.000
You've been so good to us.

23:47.480 --> 23:48.840
If I blame you

23:49.280 --> 23:50.280
or hate you,

23:51.360 --> 23:53.490
I wouldn't deserve to be a human being.

23:54.840 --> 23:56.040
Silly girl.

23:58.240 --> 23:59.520
I've already treated you

23:59.520 --> 24:01.640
as my own daughter in my heart.

24:04.520 --> 24:05.400
Yesterday,

24:06.120 --> 24:07.160
I was just,

24:10.160 --> 24:12.040
just complaining to your uncle.

24:12.040 --> 24:14.400
I didn't mean it.

24:15.360 --> 24:16.880
But you have to believe me,

24:17.200 --> 24:18.640
I never felt

24:18.640 --> 24:20.570
you and your grandma were burdens.

24:21.520 --> 24:23.200
We are family.

24:34.520 --> 24:36.050
The medical bills I owe you,

24:36.520 --> 24:38.180
I'll find a way to pay you back.

24:47.520 --> 24:48.200
By the way,

24:49.280 --> 24:50.440
as for Mutou,

24:51.800 --> 24:53.360
please don't tell him.

24:54.120 --> 24:56.250
I'm afraid it will affect his studies.

24:56.720 --> 24:58.000
I'm going to class.

24:58.920 --> 25:00.680
Qingyun already knows.

25:21.560 --> 25:23.690
Strive for the college entrance exam.

25:31.920 --> 25:34.240
The best thing about childhood sweethearts

25:34.240 --> 25:35.640
is exactly this.

25:36.240 --> 25:39.720
There's always an unspoken understanding that others wouldn't get.

25:39.720 --> 25:42.480
Regarding what happened to his parents and mine,

25:43.000 --> 25:44.640
I know he knows,

25:45.000 --> 25:46.840
and he knows I understand.

25:47.600 --> 25:49.800
But neither of us confronted the other,

25:50.280 --> 25:52.560
to avoid any awkwardness.

25:56.640 --> 25:57.760
Yuanbao.

25:58.240 --> 26:00.700
Actually, I really want to apologize to you.

26:01.200 --> 26:02.920
If it weren't for my illness,

26:03.240 --> 26:05.770
nothing would have happened to your parents.

26:06.200 --> 26:08.600
All the pain and suffering you went through

26:09.920 --> 26:11.840
should have happened to me.

26:12.400 --> 26:13.240
But now,

26:13.880 --> 26:15.280
even if I say

26:15.360 --> 26:16.960
a casual 'sorry,'

26:17.840 --> 26:19.200
what's the point?

26:27.880 --> 26:28.880
After that day,

26:29.480 --> 26:31.940
Yuanbao has been deliberately avoiding us.

26:34.720 --> 26:36.080
My mom and I didn't know

26:36.320 --> 26:38.650
how to salvage this relationship either.

26:39.320 --> 26:40.200
Many times,

26:40.520 --> 26:43.720
the more afraid you are of losing, the less you dare to try and salvage it.

26:43.720 --> 26:46.440
Without experiencing this feeling firsthand,

26:46.840 --> 26:48.240
no one could understand.

26:51.680 --> 26:52.360
Ma'am,

26:52.680 --> 26:54.880
this house of yours is really too old,

26:55.000 --> 26:56.320
and the location is poor.

26:56.320 --> 26:58.560
It's too difficult for you to sell it so urgently.

26:58.560 --> 27:00.360
How about you think it over?

27:20.080 --> 27:23.440
The hospital expenses are draining like water every day.

27:23.800 --> 27:27.160
The money we borrowed is almost gone.

27:28.360 --> 27:29.880
Even though I refused her,

27:30.320 --> 27:31.400
she still stubbornly

27:31.400 --> 27:33.600
sold all her jewelry.

27:34.360 --> 27:36.120
And she still goes to the hospital

27:36.120 --> 27:38.250
to see grandma every day without fail.

27:38.400 --> 27:41.520
How do we weigh right and wrong in many things?

27:59.760 --> 28:00.760
How is it, deskmate?

28:00.760 --> 28:01.760
Any news?

28:05.480 --> 28:06.120
Yuanbao.

28:07.680 --> 28:08.400
I'm sorry.

28:09.280 --> 28:10.280
My uncle,

28:11.240 --> 28:12.000
he said

28:13.920 --> 28:16.880
the treatment plan and advice they gave

28:17.480 --> 28:19.810
are pretty much the same as the conclusion

28:22.000 --> 28:23.860
from Jinghai People's Hospital.

28:26.640 --> 28:27.320
Yuanbao.

28:28.120 --> 28:29.180
Don't be like this.

28:31.560 --> 28:32.640
I've made up my mind.

28:32.640 --> 28:34.800
Tomorrow I'll ask Mr. Tian for a leave and go to Beijing.

28:34.800 --> 28:35.480
I'll beg my uncle in person.

28:35.480 --> 28:36.880
That won't be necessary.

28:37.280 --> 28:38.480
Thank you, deskmate.

28:39.560 --> 28:40.760
Don't say that.

28:41.800 --> 28:43.200
I couldn't even help you.

28:44.960 --> 28:46.480
I feel really bad about it.

28:47.160 --> 28:48.690
You've worked really hard.

28:49.560 --> 28:51.040
I am truly grateful to you.

28:51.880 --> 28:52.840
Actually,

28:54.840 --> 28:56.700
my father also got sick recently.

28:59.400 --> 29:00.480
What illness?

29:04.200 --> 29:05.080
Liver cancer.

29:18.400 --> 29:19.800
We both need to be strong,

29:20.280 --> 29:21.040
okay?

29:33.680 --> 29:35.320
Dr. Wang, Dr. Wang!

29:35.480 --> 29:37.540
Something is wrong with the patient!

29:38.320 --> 29:39.000
Grandma!

30:10.760 --> 30:12.290
Doctor, how is the patient?

30:12.560 --> 30:15.400
The patient's condition suddenly worsened during the surgery.

30:15.400 --> 30:16.200
I'm afraid

30:16.520 --> 30:18.450
he won't make it through the night.

31:18.280 --> 31:19.560
How is Grandpa Gong?

31:21.000 --> 31:22.530
His blood pressure is high.

31:22.840 --> 31:24.970
He is getting an IV drip in the ward now.

31:25.840 --> 31:26.970
After all, he is old,

31:27.160 --> 31:28.820
and can't handle such things.

31:35.600 --> 31:37.530
The burial plot has been arranged,

31:37.640 --> 31:39.440
right next to Tiejun and Aihua.

31:45.320 --> 31:47.320
Yuanbao.

31:51.280 --> 31:53.520
I'm here, Grandma.
